                    <h3 class="founder-title">In Memory of Jeannette R. Holtham</h3>
                    <p class="founder-subtitle">Author, President, and Founder of Youth Transformation Center</p>
                    <p class="founder-text">Jeannette was a trailblazer in Colorado’s restorative justice movement and dedicated her life to transforming the lives of high-risk youth. With over two decades of hands-on work in alternative schools, detention centers, and prisons, Jeannette impacted the lives of over 5,000 young individuals across multiple states and countries. Her legacy lives on through Youth Transformation Center, inspiring youth to reach their fullest potential. Jeannette graduated summa cum laude from Regis University with a BA in Communications, receiving the Excellence in Communication Award. We honor her vision, leadership, and unrelenting passion to make a difference.</p>
